.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL_HTLC_LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-htlc-list \- list HTLCs for a channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-htlc-list
.I <arg>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns in-flight HTLCs for the specified channel.
.PP
Output: JSON object or array from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
